metadata.name: AIdentity Game One
metadata.description:
Fake Reals vs Real Fakes. 

The game is chess. Anyone on NFT Twitter can suggest a move.

The first to reply to the board each day gets to make the move.

One move per day until there is a winner. You can play either side.

At any stage, anyone can stop the game by purchasing the board in its current state for 0.69 eth or highest offer.

If the game completes, the person who made the winning last move gets the board transferred to them as the prize.

FIRST GAME WON BY: @alex8rite playing for Real Fakes
